Description:
    Generate boilerplate files to get you up and running with stimulus_reflex

Example:
    rails generate stimulus_reflex:install demo

    # TODO: tie into railties to support bundle exec rails stimulus_reflex:install
    This will create:
        app/javascript/controllers/application_controller.js
        app/javascript/controllers/example_controller.js
        app/reflexes/application_reflex.rb
        app/javascript/controllers/example_reflex.rb

    rails generate stimulus_reflex demo

    This will create:
        app/javascript/controllers/demo_controller.js
        app/reflexes/demo_reflex.rb

    rails generate stimulus_reflex:controller demo

    This will create:
        app/javascript/controllers/demo_controller.js

    rails generate stimulus_reflex:reflex demo

    This will create:
        app/reflexes/demo_reflex.rb
